%20by%20doctors%20--%20meant%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20their%20protest%20--%20at%20puja%20pandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729532760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fq9ut12bg_kolkata-rape-murder-case_625x300_13_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-doctors-withdraw-hunger-strike-after-meet-with-mamata-banerjee-6841766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20protesting%20junior%20doctors%20of%20Bengal%20have%20withdrawn%20their%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20this%20evening.%20They%20also%20called%20off%20their%20proposed%20strike%20across%20hospitals%20due%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Skoop%20Media%20Licenses%20Crime%20Series%20%E2%80%98Mocro%20Maffia%E2%80%99%20to%20Germany%20and%20Belgium%3A%20%E2%80%98Phenomenon%20in%20Its%20Own%20Right%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729532732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmm-s5-still1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236185010%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RTL%2B%20Germany%20has%20acquired%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20the%20Dutch%20hit%20crime%20series%20%E2%80%9CMocro%20Maffia%3A%20Gangs%20of%20Amsterdam%E2%80%9D%20from%20Amsterdam-based%20distributor%20Skoop%20Media%20for%20its%20streaming%20platform.%C2%A0%20Belgian%20platform%20Streamz%20has%20also%20secured%20rights%20to%20%E2%80%9CMocro%20Maffia%E2%80%99s%E2%80%9D%20latest%20%E2%80%93%20and%20final%20%E2%80%93%20sixth%20season%2C%20along%20with%20re-licensing%20the%20series%E2%80%99%20previous%20five%20seasons%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22John%20Hopewell%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic