.%20He%20used%20to%20scold%20his%20mother%20if%20she%20came%20out%20to%20talk%20to%20anyone%20and%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months%20he%20always%20kept%20the%20house%20locked%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20neighbour%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20neighbour%20said%20Mr%20Dey%20told%20some%20people%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20fine%20and%20she%20was%20not%20interested%20in%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20To%20others%2C%20Mr%20Day%20said%20his%20mother%20was%20unwell%20and%20so%20wouldn't%20come%20out%2C%20the%20second%20neighbour%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDey%20told%20me%20his%20mother%20had%20passed%20away.%20All%20these%20contradictory%20versions%20led%20us%20to%20doubting%20him%20and%20we%20alerted%20his%20relatives%2C%20who%20called%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20neighbour%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20officer%20said%20Mr%20Dey%20told%20them%20his%20mother%20died%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20tell%20anyone%20as%20he%20was%20unwell%20and%20there%20was%20no%20relatives%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20investigate%20and%20find%20out%20what%20exactly%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729532220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fgq5f3af_guwahati-skeleton_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-assam-shocker-man-kept-mothers-decomposed-body-in-house-for-3-months-6841971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chilling%20incident%20has%20come%20to%20light%20in%20Assam's%20Guwahati%2C%20where%20the%20skeletal%20remains%20of%20a%20decomposed%20body%20of%20an%20elderly%20woman%20were%20found%20inside%20a%20house.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Resolved%2099.1%25%20of%20the%2010%2C644%20complaints%20received%20from%20CCPA%3A%20Ola%20Electric%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729532121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fresolved-99-1-of-the-10-644-complaints-received-from-ccpa-ola-electric-124102101372_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CCPA%20had%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20demanding%20an%20explanation%20for%20the%20handling%20of%20thousands%20of%20consumer%20complaints%20regarding%20service%20deficiencies%2C%20and%20providing%2015%20days%20to%20respond%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTeacher%20Tried%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Olympic%20Medallist%20Says%20She%20Was%20Sexually%20Harassed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%2C%20Oct%2021%20Olympic%20bronze%20medal-winning%20former%20wrestler%20Sakshi%20Malik%20has%20said%20that%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia's%20decision%20to%20accept%20exemption%20from%20the%20Asian%20Games%20trials%20last%20year%20hit%20the%20image%20of%20their%20protest%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20as%20it%20made%20their%20movement%20seem%20%26quot%3Bselfish%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Sakshi%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20prominent%20faces%20of%20the%20prolonged%20protest%2C%20made%20this%20statement%20in%20her%20recently-released%20book%20'Witness'.%20The%2032-year-old%20from%20Haryana%20also%20said%20she%20was%20molested%20in%20her%20childhood%20by%20a%20tuition%20teacher%20but%20she%20kept%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20not%20tell%20my%20family%20about%20it%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20my%20fault.%20My%20tuition%20teacher%20from%20my%20school%20days%20used%20to%20harass%20me.%20He%20would%20call%20me%20over%20to%20his%20place%20for%20classes%20at%20odd%20times%20and%20sometimes%20tried%20to%20touch%20me.%20I%20was%20scared%20to%20go%20for%20my%20tuition%20classes%20but%20I%20could%20never%20tell%20my%20mom.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20struggles%20at%20the%20start%20of%20her%20career%2C%20Sakshi%20said%20she%20hated%20confrontations%20and%20would%20think%20of%20running%20away%20from%20her%20bouts%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20her%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20fear%20that%20I've%20carried%20to%20the%20end%20of%20my%20career.%20I've%20never%20enjoyed%20the%20actual%20act%20of%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20was%20an%20exceptionally%20slow%20starter%20in%20wrestling.%20I%20won%20my%20first%20bout%20only%20after%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20my%20first%20stepping%20on%20a%20wrestling%20mat.%20It%20wasn't%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20physical%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20always%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20and%20strongest%20girls%20at%20my%20coaching%20centre%20for%20my%20age.%20But%20I%20never%20developed%20the%20fearlessness%20you%20needed%20for%20a%20fight.%20I%20would%20always%20get%20very%20nervous%20before%20my%20bouts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20was%20a%20picture%20of%20defiance%20during%20the%20protest%20against%20Sharan%20Singh%20and%20said%20the%20political%20class%20disappointed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20alleged%20that%20former%20wrestler%20Babita%20Phogat%2C%20who%20is%20now%20a%20BJP%20politician%2C%20had%20selfish%20motives%20even%20though%20she%20portrayed%20herself%20as%20a%20well-wisher%20for%20the%20protesting%20trio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20hindsight%2C%20while%20I%20know%20that%20ending%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20reign%20was%20the%20primary%20goal%20for%20Vinesh%20and%20Bajrang%2C%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20thinking%20that%20that%20was%20Babita's%20sole%20intention%20too....She%20didn't%20just%20want%20to%20just%20get%20rid%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20she%20wanted%20to%20replace%20him.%26quot%3B%20Babita%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20immediately%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20