try%20Links%20To%20Combat%20Job%20Disruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%2C%20a%20key%20session%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Role%20of%20Education%20in%20Shaping%20India's%20Century%26quot%3B%20brought%20forward%20discussions%20on%20how%20technology%20and%20education%20can%20shape%20India's%20workforce%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20preparing%20students%20to%20be%20industry-ready.%20Educationists%20from%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%20highlighted%20how%20the%20integration%20of%20real-world%20problems%2C%20interdisciplinary%20research%2C%20and%20technological%20advancements%20are%20central%20to%20their%20educational%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Balakrishnan%20Shankar%2C%20Dean%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Engineering%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%2C%20detailed%20the%20university's%20unique%20%26quot%3BLiving%20Lab%26quot%3B%20programme%2C%20where%20students%20are%20actively%20involved%20in%20solving%20critical%20problems%20in%20rural%20areas%20across%20India.%20%26quot%3BOur%20parent%20organisation%20has%20adopted%20around%20100%20villages%2C%20where%20students%20identify%20real-life%20issues%2C%20work%20on%20cost-effective%20solutions%2C%20and%20deploy%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Shankar%20said.%20This%20hands-on%20approach%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20200%20patents%20being%20filed%20by%20students%20and%20faculty%2C%20with%20100%20of%20them%20already%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20shared%20a%20key%20example%20of%20the%20university's%20impact%20when%20they%20set%20up%20a%20wireless%20network%20centre%20in%20Munnar%2C%20a%20region%20prone%20to%20landslides.%20%26quot%3BWe%20identified%20a%20village%2C%20deployed%20sensors%2C%20and%20predicted%20landslides%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20evacuation%20of%20villagers%20twice%2C%20ultimately%20saving%20lives.%20This%20centre%20is%20now%20recognised%20for%20excellence%20in%20detecting%20landslides%2C%26quot%3B%20Shankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20role%20of%20compassion-driven%20research%2C%20Dr%20Shankar%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20motive%20is%20to%20solve%20the%20common%20man's%20problems%20through%20interdisciplinary%20efforts%2C%20leveraging%20AI%20and%20other%20technologies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20Kodoor%2C%20Director%20of%20Academia-Industry%20Partnership%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%2C%20said%20that%20AI%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20disruptor%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20driving%20the%20need%20for%20a%20workforce%20with%20new%2C%20future-ready%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReinforced%20this%20point%20by%20discussing%20AI's%20profound%20impact%20on%20the%20job%20market%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20estimated%20to%20replace%2085%20million%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%20while%20creating%20100%20million%20new%20ones%20requiring%20different%20skill%20sets.%20Automation%20has%20always%20replaced%20jobs%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20it's%20targeting%20roles%20that%20require%20cognitive%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kodoor%20explained.%20He%20stressed%20that%20educational%20institutions%20must%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20industries%20to%20prepare%20students%20for%20the%20jobs%20of%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20this%20vision%2C%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%20has%20signed%20over%20100%20Memorandums%20of%20Understanding%20(MoUs)%20with%20various%20industries%2C%20including%20the%20automotive%2C%20energy%2C%20IT%2C%20and%20construction%20sectors.%20%26quot%3BOur%20students%20work%20on%20real-time%20industry%20projects%2C%20go%20for%20internships%2C%20and%20gain%20practical%20exposure%20to%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20business%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kodoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20among%20students%2C%20both%20Dr%20Shankar%20and%20Mr%20Kodoor%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20universities%20to%20move%20beyond%20just%20being%20centres%20of%20knowl