a%3Elike%20dried%20powder%20and%20pulp.%20With%20jackfruits%20easily%20available%20in%20abundance%20not%20only%20in%20my%20backyard%20but%20throughout%20the%20region%2C%20and%20with%20a%20dryer%20already%20at%20home%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20establish%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20my%20perception%20of%20jackfruits%20changed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20with%20jackfruit%20products%2C%20Rani%20established%20her%20place%20in%20the%20local%20market%20with%20the%20support%20of%20local%20officials.%20Through%20her%20brand%20Eden%20Jackfruit%20Products%2C%20Rani%20leveraged%20white%20labelling%20to%20bring%20high-quality%20jackfruit-based%20products%20to%20the%20market.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20focused%20on%20building%20a%20website%20and%20establishing%20a%20strong%20presence%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Rani%20sources%20jackfruits%20from%2020%20neighbours%2C%20paying%20them%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20produce%20while%20employing%2010%20workers%20to%20help%20process%20the%20fruits.%20Through%20value-addition%2C%20Rani%20earns%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20home%2C%20work%2C%20and%20entrepreneurial%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20journey%20of%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur%20from%20a%20homemaker%2C%20Rani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20childhood%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20loved%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20Here%2C%20my%20day%20starts%20at%205%20am%2C%20and%20I%20manage%20all%20household%20responsibilities%20before%20devoting%20my%20day%20to%20overseeing%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20factory%20and%20working%20with%20Kudumbashree.%20The%20busy%20schedule%20keeps%20me%20motivated%2C%20and%20when%20I%20retire%20to%20bed%20at%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20unwavering%20dedication%20also%20inspires%20t