ms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKing%20Charles%20faced%20a%20verbal%20attack%20by%20indigenous%20senator%20Lidia%20Thorpe%20during%20his%20Australian%20parliament%20speech%20as%20the%20senator%20called%20him%20to%20return%20indigenous%20remains%20and%20land.%20Explaining%20her%20action%2C%20Thorpe%20told%20Sky%20News%20that%20Charles%20should%20answer%20for%20the%20thousands%20of%20massacre%20sited%20in%20Australia.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20our%20bones%20and%20our%20skulls%20still%20in%20his%20possession%20--%20or%20in%20his%20family's%20possession.%20We%20want%20that%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senator%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fthey-have-our-skulls-why-australia-senator-lidia-thorpe-heckled-king-charles%2Farticleshow%2F114430771.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fthey-have-our-skulls-why-australia-senator-lidia-thorpe-heckled-king-charles%2Famp_articleshow%2F114430771.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fthey-have-our-skulls-why-australia-senator-lidia-thorpe-heckled-king-charles%2Famp_articleshow%2F114430771.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20Explains%20Why%20Russia%20Will%20Remain%20India's%20Strategic%20Partner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20spoke%20about%20'The%20India%20Century'%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20During%20the%20interaction%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20gave%20a%20detailed%20overview%20on%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20and%20how%20it%20is%20playing%20an%20increasingly%20global%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20World%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20discussed%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20ties%20-%20from%20the%20US%20and%20China%20to%20Russia%20and%20India's%20neighbourhood.%20He%20even%20spoke%20a%20few%20lines%20about%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20Russia%20relationship%2C%20the%20foreign%20minister%20made%20it%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20India's%20relationship%20with%20Russia%20is%20time-tested%20and%20among%20the%20most%20important.%20Explaining%20his%20point%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20put%20it%20to%20you%20very%20simply.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20our%20history%20with%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20and%20subsequently%20Russia%20since%20Independence%20in%201947%2C%20I%20can%20say%20with%20confidence%20and%20knowing%20that%20nobody%20in%20this%20room%20can%20contradict%20it%2C%20that%20Russia%20has%20never%20done%20anything%20to%20impact%20India's%20interest%20negatively%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20in%20geopolitics%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20is%20a%20big%20statement%20to%20make%20because%20there%20are%20not%20many%20major%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20for%20whom%20such%20a%20statement%20can%20be%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20told%20NDTV%20World%20that%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Russia's%20situation%20is%20different%20and%20Russia's%20relationship%20with%20the%20West%20has%20broken%20down.%20We%20now%20have%20a%20Russia%20which%20is%20turning%20much%20more%20towards%20Asia%20(than%20Europe%20and%20the%20West)%2C%20so%20we%20must%20ask%20ourselves%20that%20if%20Russia%20is%20looking%20more%20at%20Asia%2C%20should%20Russia%20not%20have%20multiple%20options%20in%20Asia%3F%20And%20as%20an%20Asian%20country%2C%20should%20we%20(India)%20not%20do%20in%20Asia%20that%20which%20is%20in%20our%20national%20interest%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20Russia%20as%20a%20major%20natural%20resources%20power%20has%20a%20complementarity%20with%20India%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20development%20when%20we%20are%20big%20resource%20consumers.%20People%20talk%20about%20Russian%20oil%2C%20but%20it%20isn%3Bt%20just%20about%20oil.%20It%20could%20be%20about%20fertilizers%2C%20metal%2C%20coal%2C%20etc.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20big%20economic%20logic%20to%20it%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20besides%20an%20economic%20relationship%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20strategic%20one.%20He%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20basic%20strategic%20logic%20-%20that%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20Eurasian%20landmass%2C%20there%20are%203%20big%20countries%20(Russia%2C%20China%20and%20India).%20It%20is%20a%20one-o-one%20in%20international%20relations%2C%20that%20a%20country%20will%20always%20maintain%20the%20balance%20in%20relationship%20with%20the%20country%20which%20is%20your%20immediate%20neighbour's%20neighbour%20-%20and%20do%20so%20in%20very%20good%20stead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strategic%20logic%2C%20there%20is%20an%20economic%20fit%2C%20and%20the%20relationship%20overall%20has%20had%20a%20very%20positive%20history%2C%20so%20that%20is%20how%20it%20is%20viewed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20reiterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBREAKTHROUGH%20WITH%20CHINA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20today%20added%20to%20what%20India's%20foreign%20secretary%20said%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20outcome%26quot%3B%20emerging%20from%20the%20standoff%20with%20China%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20saying%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20soldiers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20resume%20patrolling%20in%20the%20way%20they%20had%20been%20doing%20before%20the%20border%20face-off%20began%20in%20May%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20announced%20India%20and%20China%20have%20arrived%20on%20a%20patrolling%20arrangement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20and%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20disengagement%20and%20resolution%20of%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20patrolling%2C%20and%20we%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20the%202020%20position.%20With%20that%20we%20can%20say%20the%20disengagement%20with%20China%20has%20been%20completed.%20Details%20will%20come%20out%20in%20due%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20areas%20which%20for%20various%20reasons%20after%202020%2C%20they%20blocked%20us%2C%20we%20blocked%20them.%20We%20have%20now%20reached%20an%20understanding%20which%20will%20allow%20patrolling%20as%20we%20had%20been%20doing%20till%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20came%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Russia%20to%20attend%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA'S%20NEIGHBOURHOOD%20FIRST%20POLICY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20India's%20highest%20priority%20has%20always%20been%20about%20fostering%20good%20relations%20with%20its%20neighbours%2C%20Mr%20Jaishanakr%20emphasised%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20always%20played%20a%20positive%20and%20friendly%20part%20towards%20its%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20examples%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20even%20Maldives%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20foreign%20minister%20gave%20examples%20of%20how%20India%20has%20always%20tried%20to%20build%20a%20neighbourhood%20of%20cooperation%20and%20camaraderie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20this%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20%26quot%3BOur%20neighbourhood%20is%20democratic%20which%20means%20that%20political%20changes%20will%20keep%20on%20happening.%20We%20will%20often%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20their%20politics.%20We%20have%20to%20factor%20in%20that%20in%20our%20policies.%20If%20we%20can%20create%20a%20record%20of%20being%20a%20country%20which%20is%20a%20reliable%20friend%20in%20any%20trouble%2C%20if%20they%20understand%20that%20there's%20this%20country%20India%20which%20is%20generous%2C%20which%20is%20large%2C%20if%20we%20create%20that%20record%20and%20which%20I%20feel%20we%20have.%20During%20Sri%20Lanka%20crisis%2C%20we%20stepped%20up.%20Today%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20very%20big%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20S%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBhutan%20had%20the%20wisdom%20to%20collaborate%20on%20electricity.%20This%20is%20a%20lesson%20which%20everyone%20should%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20praising%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20'JUSTIN%20TRUDEAU'%20PROBLEM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20ties%20with%20Canada%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20Justin%20Trudeau%20government%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20Indian%20diplomats%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20there%20in%20relation%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20Trudeau%20government's%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20standards%26quot%3B%20and%20stressing%20that%20saying%20so%20is%20an%20understatement%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20different%20standards%20for%20how%20they%20behave%20domestically%20and%20how%20they%20behave%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20asked%20us%20to%20subject%20our%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20a%20police%20inquiry%20and%20we%20chose%20to%20withdraw%20our%20High%20Commissioner...%20They%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20our%20diplomats%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Canada%20which%20directly%20pertain%20to%20their%20welfare%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20license%20they%20give%20themselves%20is%20%26quot%3Btotally%20different%20from%20the%20restrictions%20they%20impose%20on%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCanadian%20diplomats%20have%20no%20problem%20going%20around%20on%20our%20military%20or%20our%20police%2C%20profiling%20people%2C%20targeting%20people%20to%20be%20stopped%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20have%20people%20openly%20threatening%20Indian%20leaders%20and%20diplomats%2C%20their%20response%20is%20freedom%20of%20speech...%20If%20you%20threaten%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%2C%20he%20is%20supposed%20to%20accept%20it%20as%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20if%20an%20Indian%20journalist%20says%20the%20Canadian%20High%20Commissioner%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20South%20Block%20looking%20very%20grumpy%2C%20it%20is%20apparently%20foreign%20interference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVISIT%20TO%20PAKISTAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20interaction%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20a%20line%20about%20Pakistan.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20good%20SCO%20member.%20We%20were%20very%20supportive%20of%20Pakistan's%20presidency%20this%20year%20and%20wanted%20the%20proceeding%20to%20be%20smooth.%20Haath%20milaya%20aur%20aa%20gaye%20wapis%20(shook%20hands%20and%20came%20back)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20summing%20up%20his%20visit%20to%20Islamabad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729515240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F38l4dd4_s-jaishankar_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-world-summit-s-jaishankar-explains-why-russia-will-remain-indias-strategic-partner-6839984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20today%20spoke%20about%20'The%20India%20Century'%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20During%20the%20interaction%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20gave%20a%20detailed%20overview%20on%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20and%20how%20it%20is%20playing%20an%20increasingly%20global%20role.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-world-summit-s-jaishankar-explains-why-russia-will-remain-indias-strategic-partner-6839984%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDouble%20Standards%20A%20Very%20Mild%20Word%20For%20It%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20Canada%20Stance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanadians%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20Indian%20diplomats%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20there%20in%20relation%20to%20India%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20today%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit.%20%C2%A0In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20of%20the%20different%20standards%20--%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20standards%20is%20a%20very%20mild%20word%20for%20it%26quot%3B%20--%20%C2%A0that%20seem%20to%20exist%20between%20how%20Canada%20treats%20other%20diplomats%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Blicense'%20their%20diplomats%20allow%20themselves%20while%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Canada-India%20political%20ties%20that%20have%20nosedived%20following%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20about%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20attributed%20it%20to%20several%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20the%20changing%20world%20order%20where%20the%20western%20world%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20adjust%20to%20developing%20nations%20that%20surged%20ahead%20and%20stand%20on%20an%20equal%20platform.%20Besides%20this%20'big%20picture%26quot%3B%20reason%20are%20conditions%20that%20are%20specific%20to%20Canada-India%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20relations%20are%20extremely%20strong%20in%20terms%20of%20trade%20or%20people-to-people%20connection%2C%20politically%2C%20things%20changed%20just%20when%20the%20two%20nations%20have%20emerged%20from%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%201985%20bombing%20of%20Kanishka%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20182%20flight%20from%20Montreal.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20lowest%20point%20of%20that%20relationship%20--%20tit-for-tat%20expulsions%20of%20diplomats%20--%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20asked%20us%20to%20subject%20our%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20a%20police%20inquiry%20and%20we%20chose%20to%20withdraw%20our%20High%20Commissioner...%20They%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20our%20diplomats%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Canada%20which%20directly%20pertain%20to%20their%20welfare%20and%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20license%20they%20give%20themselves%20is%20%26quot%3Btotally%20different%20from%20the%20restrictions%20they%20impose%20on%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCanadian%20diplomats%20have%20no%20problem%20going%20around%20on%20our%20military%20or%20our%20police%2C%20profiling%20people%2C%20targeting%20people%20to%20be%20stopped%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20have%20people%20openly%20threatening%20Indian%20leaders%20and%20diplomats%2C%20their%20response%20is%20freedom%20of%20speech...%20If%20you%20threaten%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%2C%20he%20is%20supposed%20to%20accept%20it%20as%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20if%20an%20Indian%20journalist%20says%20the%20Canadian%20High%20Commissioner%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20South%20Block%20looking%20very%20grumpy%2C%20it%20is%20apparently%20foreign%20interference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20--%20on%20a%20downward%20spiral%20since%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20in%20September%20last%20year%20--%20have%20plummeted%20after%20the%20series%20of%20fresh%20allegations%20against%20the%20Indian%20envoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Ministry%20slammed%20Ottawa%20for%20its%20allegations%20against%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20--%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20senior-most%20diplomats%20who%20served%20in%20Japan%2C%20Sudan%2C%20Italy%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%2C%20India%20said%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%26quot%3B%20and%20deserved%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20contempt.%20New%20Delhi%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20faith%20in%20the%20current%20Canadian%20Government's%20commitment%20to%20ensure%20their%20security%26quot%3B.%20The%20ministry%20had%20also%20recalled%20the%20diplomats%2C%20after%20which%20Canada%20formally%20expelled%20them.%20%C2%A0India%20reiterated%20by%20ordering%20out%20six%20Canadian%20diplomats.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20in%20a%20startling%20admission%20during%20a%20public%20inquiry%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau%20had%20admitted%20that%20Canada%20had%20no%20%26quot%3Bhard%20evidentiary%20proof%26quot%3B%20in%202023%20to%20support%20allegations%20linking%20Indian%20government%20agents%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20His%20claims%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau%20admitted%2C%20were%20based%20on%20intelligence%20rather%20than%20hard%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20briefed%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20intelligence%20from%20Canada%2C%20and%20possibly%20from%20Five%20Eyes%20allies%20that%20made%20it%20fairly%20clear%2C%20incredibly%20clear%2C%20that%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20this...%20Agents%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20on%20Canadian%20soil%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729515180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fgv1i0t28_s-jaishankar_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-to-imagine-current-state-of-relations-s-jaishankar-on-canada-ties-6839070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canadians%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20Indian%20diplomats%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20there%20in%20relation%20to%20India%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20today%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdifficult-to-imagine-current-state-of-relations-s-jaishankar-on-canada-ties-6839070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBack%20To%202020%20Patrolling%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20To%20NDTV%20On%20India%2C%20China%20Pact%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20and%20Chinese%20soldiers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20resume%20patrolling%20in%20the%20way%20they%20had%20been%20doing%20before%20the%20border%20face-off%20began%20in%20May%202020%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20today%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20announced%20India%20and%20China%20have%20arrived%20on%20a%20patrolling%20arrangement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20and%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20disengagement%20and%20resolution%20of%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20came%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Russia%20to%20attend%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20patrolling%2C%20and%20we%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20the%202020%20position.%20With%20that%20we%20can%20say%20the%20disengagement%20with%20China%20has%20been%20completed.%20Details%20will%20come%20out%20in%20due%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20areas%20which%20for%20various%20reasons%20after%202020%2C%20they%20blocked%20us%2C%20we%20blocked%20them.%20We%20have%20now%20reached%20an%20understanding%20which%20will%20allow%20patrolling%20as%20we%20had%20been%20doing%20till%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20the%20LAC%20breakthrough%20is%20a%20good%20development%20that%20happened%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpatient%20and%20persevering%20diplomacy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-agree-on-patrolling-agreement-along-lac-leads-to-disengagement-6838489%5C%22%3EIndia%20To%20Resume%20Patrolling%20In%20Ladakh%20After%20Big%20Breakthrough%20With%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20At%20various%20points%20of%20time%20people%20almost%20gave%20up.%20We%20have%20always%20maintained%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20we%20obviously%20had%20to%20do%20counter%20deployment%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20negotiating%20since%20September%202020.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20very%20patient%20process%2C%20though%20more%20complicated%20than%20how%20it%20should%20have%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fqcr6vjes_ladakh-generic_625x300_10_September_20.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20important%20thing%20is%20if%20we%20have%20reached%20an%20understanding%2C%20I%20think%20what%20it%20does%20is%20it%20creates%20a%20basis%20for%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20along%20the%20border%2C%20which%20were%20there%20before%202020.%20That%20was%20a%20major%20concern.%20If%20there%20is%20no%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%2C%20how%20can%20other%20areas%20of%20bilateral%20ties%20improve%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20agreed%20people%20may%20speculate%20on%20the%20LAC%20development%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20he%20would%20use%20%26quot%3Bcaution%26quot%3B%20in%20responding%20on%20whether%20this%20positive%20development%20would%20spread%20to%20trade%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(LAC%20breakthrough)%20has%20just%20happened.%20I%20would%20not%20go%20so%20fast%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20working%20mechanism%20for%20consultation%20and%20coordination%20on%20India-China%20border%20affairs%20was%20held%20on%20August%2029%20in%20Beijing.%20The%20two%20sides%20then%20had%20a%20frank%2C%20constructive%20and%20forward-looking%20exchange%20of%20views%20on%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20to%20narrow%20down%20differences%20and%20find%20early%20resolution%20of%20outstanding%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20agreed%20that%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%2C%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20LAC%20are%20the%20essential%20basis%20for%20restoration%20of%20normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20had%20said%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20resolved%20the%20%26quot%3Blow-hanging%20fruits%26quot%3B%20and%20now%20need%20to%20address%20difficult%20situations%2C%20adding%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20signalling%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20diplomatic%20side%20and%20execution%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20dependent%20on%20military%20commanders%20of%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20and%20Chinese%20military%20commanders%20too%20had%20been%20meeting%20regularly%20seeking%20complete%20disengagement%20in%20the%20remaining%20areas%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20as%20an%20essential%20basis%20for%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20India-China%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20still%20remained%20to%20be%20de-es