3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20broke%20our%20mental%20barrier%20regarding%20what%20people%20expect%2C%20our%20content%20took%20off.%20People%20want%20raw%2C%20real%20knowledge.%20We%20started%20shooting%20in%20our%20warehouse%20with%20toys%20in%20the%20background%2C%20and%20it%20worked%20like%20a%20charm%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20consistently%20creating%20content%2C%20Haripriya%20cracked%20the%20code%20for%20success%20and%20has%20never%20looked%20back.%20Building%20trust%20is%20paramount%2C%20she%20stresses%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20is%20rule%20number%20one%20in%20establishing%20a%20successful%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20begin%20paid%20marketing%20until%20they%20reached%201%2C50%2C000%20followers%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20organic%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20D2C%20business%2C%20trust-building%20is%20most%20important%20and%20can%20happen%20only%20through%20organic%20sales%20in%20the%20beginning.%20My%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20a%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20which%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haripriya%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20nearly%205%2C00%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20and%20receive%20over%2015%2C000%20orders%20a%20month.%20Their%20toys%20start%20from%20Rs%2049%20to%20Rs%208%2C000%20and%20include%20educational%20toys%2C%20family%20games%2C%20open-ended%20toys%2C%20pretend%20play%20items%2C%20magnatiles%2C%20kinetic%20sand%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20Their%20bestsellers%20include%20puzzles%2C%20memory%20card%20games%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CShut%20the%20Box.%E2%80%9D%20Haripriya%20adds%20that%20most%20of%20the%20toys%20are%20open%20ended%2C%20meaning%20children%20of%20various%20age%20groups%20can%20play%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Have%20a%20vision%20and%20take%20calculated%20risks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20moment%20for%20Haripriya%20