w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-1-Deena-Binod-1728640192-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-1-Deena-Binod-1728640192-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDeena%20Talbot%20and%20Binod%20Aryal%20with%20the%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20these%20dogs%2C%20they%20are%20housed%20in%20different%20pens.%20For%20instance%2C%20older%20dogs%20and%20dogs%20receiving%20medication%20and%20treatments%20are%20grouped%20in%20the%20largest%20pen%20measuring%20100%20x%20100%20feet.%20Dogs%20which%20are%20younger%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20more%20active%2C%20are%20housed%20in%20a%20separate%20pen.%C2%A0Young%20pups%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20grouped%20in%20another%20pen.%20One%20pen%20is%20specifically%20dedicated%20to%20a%20Tibetan%20Mastiff.%20On%20the%20outside%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20aggressive%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20owner%20had%20to%20surrender%20him%20because%20he%20had%20bitten%20several%20people.%20We%20gave%20him%20his%20own%20pen%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20female%20dogs%2C%20and%20he%20gets%20along%20fine%20with%20them%20and%20the%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESemchan%E2%80%99s%20unique%20approach%20to%20stray%20dog%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20rescue%20service%20has%20become%20pretty%20well-known%20in%20Leh.%20Our%20phone%20number%20is%20available%20in%20the%20community%2C%20so%20people%20call%20the%20team.%20The%20caller%20is%20asked%20to%20send%20a%20picture%20or%20video%20of%20the%20dog%20needing%20rescue%20and%20to%20stay%20there%20with%20the%20dog%20while%20we%20come.%20Usually%2C%20two%20men%20take%20the%20van%2C%20which%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20cage%20for%20capturing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20uses%20careful%20and%20compassionate%20capture%20methods%2C%20almost%20always%20without%20nets%20or%20ropes.%20They%20usually%20cover%20the%20dog%20with%20a%20blanket%2C%20scoop%20it%20up%20into%20their%20arms%2C%20and%20quickly%20put%20it%20into%20the%20cage.%20Then%20we%20take%20the%20dog%20to%20the%20government%20veterinary%20hospital%20for%20examination%20and%2For%20treatment.%20Once%20the%20vets%20release%20the%20dog%20for%20aftercare%2C%20we%20bring%20it%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328239%2Fanimal-rescue-and-rehabilitation-centres-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Rescue%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ARC)%2C%20where%20we%20follow%20up%20with%20the%20prescribed%20medications%2C%20nutrition%2C%20rest%2C%20and%20safety%2C%20and%20follow-up%20visits%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Injured%20stray%20dogs%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSe