0that%20seemed%20doable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20UPSC%20tests%20your%20abilities%20in%20every%20section.%20You%20cannot%20choose%20to%20opt-out%20of%20topics%20that%20you%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with.%20In%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20I%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20gave%20equal%20weight%20to%20all%20three%20sections.%20That%20is%20what%20UPSC%20expects%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not%20neglect%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20presented%20by%20this%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362685%2Fhow-to-clear-upsc-cse-from-home-irms-officer-akash-chavda-prep-journey-delhi-coaching-busting-myths%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UPSC%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karamveer%20strategically%20adjusted%20his%20preparation%20approach.%20He%20dedicated%20about%20three%20hours%20of%20study%20each%20day%20for%20three%20months%20to%20excel%20in%20this%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20merely%20attempting%20more%20comprehension%20questions%20was%20not%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20questions%20on%20basics%20like%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20profit%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20percentages%20are%20designed%20to%20challenge%20even%20IIT%20students.%20To%20ace%20both%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning%2C%20I%20started%20referring%20to%20notes%20meant%20for%20the%20CAT%20(Common%20Admission%20Test)%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20also%20began%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys.%20This%20analysis%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20type%20of%20questions%20to%20expect%20in%20the%20exam.%20By%20focusing%20on%20all%20three%20sections%20of%20the%20CSAT%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20questions%20he%20attempted.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20says%2C%20he%20could%20score%2090%20out%20of%20the%20200%20marks%20in%20the%20exam%20on%20his%20third%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20perseverance%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20strategic%20planning%20in%20overcoming%20challenges%20and%20achieving%20one%E2%80%99s%20goals.%20His%20journey%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20well-rounded%20preparation%20strategy%20that%20encompasses%20not%20only%20a%20strong%20grasp%20of%20the%20subject%20matter%20but%20also%20a%20keen%20understanding%20of%20the%20exam%E2%80%99s%20specific%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20photos%3A%20Karamveer%20Narwaniya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728892315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20failing%20in%20UPSC-CSAT%2C%20IRMS%20officer%20Karamveer%20Narwaniya%20changed%20his%20strategy%20to%20become%20a%20UPSC%20success%20story.%20He%20shares%20expert%20tips%20to%20crack%20UPSC%20CSE%20and%20CSAT%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369549%2Firms-officer-karamveer-narwaniya-cleared-upsc-cse-shares-tips-to-clear-qualifying-csat-paper%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starbucks%20Could%20Owe%20Millions%20To%20Baristas%20Who%20Unionized%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20new%20federal%20complaint%20alleges%20the%20chain%20slashed%20workers'%20schedules%20without%20bargaining.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728669115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F67094ece26000033006cfdc7.jpeg%3Fcache%3DCPOUnij0tG%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fstarbucks-baris