0Dragonfruit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20serene%20countryside%20of%20Kadaba%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Mangaluru%2C%20amidst%20lush%20green%20fields%20and%20swaying%20coconut%20palms%2C%20lies%20a%20farm%20painted%20in%20the%20vibrant%20colours%20of%20exotic%20fruits.%20The%20red%20and%20green%20rambutans%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20dark%20purple%20mangosteens%2C%20often%20beckon%20passers-by%20with%20a%20story%20of%20resilience%20and%20success.%20Together%2C%20they%20generate%20nearly%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20annual%20revenue%20for%2042-year-old%20Lohith%20Shetty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20farming%20family%2C%20Lohith%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20one%20of%20rags%20to%20riches.%20He%20saw%20his%20father%20and%20uncles%20toil%20on%20their%2021-acre%20farm%2C%20growing%20rubber%2C%20coconuts%2C%20areca%20nuts%20and%20cashews.%20Despite%20having%20bigger%20aspirations%20as%20a%20child%2C%20financial%20challenges%20led%20him%20to%20discontinue%20his%20education%20after%20Class%2010%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20finding%20ways%20to%20supplement%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20different%20businesses%2C%20including%20a%20small%20shop%20and%20a%20restaurant%2C%20Lohith%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20millionaire%20would%20begin%20when%20he%20travelled%20to%20Dharmasthala%20to%20work%20on%20a%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExotic%20fruits%2C%20new%20beginnings%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20for%20his%20family%2C%20Lohith%20took%20up%20a%20job%20at%20a%20stone%20quarry.%20While%20he%20was%20working%20there%2C%20he%20would%20get%20a%20work%20reference%20from%20a%20friend%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reference%20that%20would%20change%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20Lohith%E2%80%99s%20job%20at%20a%20farm%20in%20Dharmasthala%2C%20about%20an%20hour%E2%80%99s%20dri