osteen.%20I%20got%20an%20idea%20about%20how%20these%20fruits%20are%20grown%2C%20where%20they%20come%20from%2C%20the%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20their%20growth%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lohith%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20in%202016%20with%20his%20newfound%20knowledge%2C%20refined%20through%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20Lohith%20decided%20to%20transform%20his%20expertise%20into%20a%20profitable%20enterprise.%20Along%20with%20him%2C%20he%20had%20brought%20back%20a%20bunch%20of%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%20and%20dragon%20fruit%20seeds%20and%20cuttings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20by%20leasing%2020%20acres%20of%20land.%20With%20the%2021%20acres%20his%20family%20already%20owned%2C%20he%20now%20had%2041%20acres%20to%20work%20with.%20The%20next%20step%20was%20to%20source%20more%20plants%2C%20which%20he%20did%20from%20a%20nursery%20in%20Kerala.%20In%20the%20next%20eight%20years%2C%20Lohith%20steadily%20capitalised%20on%20his%20advantage%20of%20being%20one%20of%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292932%2Fkarnataka-farmer-anil-balanja-grows-700-varieties-of-exotic-fruits-viral-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowers%20of%20exotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20apart%20from%20catering%20to%20his%20own%20farm%20and%20nursery%2C%20Lohith%20also%20helps%20people%20interested%20in%20growing%20such%20crops%20and%20vegetables.%20His%20ventures%20help%20him%20earn%20over%20Rs%201%20crore%20every%20year.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%20oasis%3A%20Creating%20the%20perfect%20environment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%20and%20dragon%20fruit%20are%20usually%20grown%20in%20Kerala%2C%20and%20sell%20for%20high%20prices%2C%20earning%20farmers%20a%20hefty%20profit.%20However%2C%20without%20the%20right%20conditions%2C%20yielding%20a%20good%20crop%20might%20become%20a%20tricky%20affair.%20Like%20any%20other%20plants%2C%20water%2C%20sunlight%2C%20and%20shade%20are%20key%20to%20growing%20such%20fruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRambutan%20needs%20more%20humidity%20to%20survive.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20grow%20in%20very%20hot%20areas.%20Dragon%20fruit%20and%20rambutan%20don%E2%80%99t%20grow%20in%20shade.%20You%20need%20to%20create%20the%20perfect%20environment%20for%20it.%20Mangosteen%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20grows%20well%20with%20shade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lohith%20explains%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20water%20is%20also%20imperative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lohith%20at%20his%20farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-87-1728642634-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369912%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELohith%20at%20his%20farm%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20plants%20yield%20good%20harvests%20three%20years%20after%20they%20are%20first%20planted.%20One%20rambutan%20plant%20produces%20